%20areas%20of%20both%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%202%2C500%20US%20troops%20remain%20stationed%20in%20Iraq%20to%20support%20counterterrorism%20efforts%20and%20train%20Iraqi%20forces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742013600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8kttf8rg_us-air-strike-_625x300_15_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fabdallah-makki-muslih-al-rifai-isis-abu-khadijah-death-from-above-us-missile-strike-wipes-out-isis-chief-of-global-ops-7927169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20Iraqi%20Intelligence%20and%20Security%20Forces%2C%20announced%20the%20killing%20of%20Abdallah%20Makki%20Muslih%20al-Rifai%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BAbu%20Khadijah%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20precision%20airstrike%20in%20Iraq's%20Al%20Anbar%20Province.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fabdallah-makki-muslih-al-rifai-isis-abu-khadijah-death-from-above-us-missile-strike-wipes-out-isis-chief-of-global-ops-7927169%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20International%20Airlines%20flight%20lands%20in%20Lahore%20with%20a%20missing%20wheel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742012226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119031293%2Cimgsize-705492.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-international-airlines-flight-lands-in-lahore-with-one-rear-wheel-missing%2Farticleshow%2F119030952.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Pakistan%20International%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Karachi%20to%20Lahore%20landed%20with%20one%20of%20its%20rear%20wheel%20missing%2C%20which%20was%20discovered%20upon%20arrival%2C%20after%20the%20flight%20a%20normal%20landing.%20Officials%20are%20investigating%20whether%20the%20wheel%20was%20l