7vAc%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20a%20ship%20or%20something%20in%20trouble%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20there%20will%20be%20an%20oil%20tanker%20problem%20coming%20up%20soon.%20It%20was%20a%20ship%20of%20some%20sort%20in%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20an%20oil%20tanker%2C%20maybe%20it's%20passenger%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20there%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20pollution%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Stena%20Immaculate%20was%20stationary%20and%20at%20anchor%20while%20waiting%20for%20a%20spot%20to%20open%20at%20the%20Port%20of%20Killingholme%2C%20on%20the%20River%20Humber%2C%20when%20it%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20smaller%20MV%20Solong%2C%20causing%20huge%20fires%20and%20explosions.%20Such%20was%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20blast%20that%20smoke%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20space.%20Rescuers%20managed%20to%20save%2013%20crewmembers%20from%20the%20Solong%20while%20one%20was%20presumed%20dead.%20Meanwhile%2C%20all%2013%20crewmembers%20of%20the%20Stena%20Immaculate%20were%20rescued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnostradamus-predictions-for-2025-asteroid-collision-to-plague-like-outbreak-and-more-7212856%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Nostradamus'%20Predictions%20For%202025%3A%20Asteroid%20Collision%20To%20Plague-Like%20Outbreak%20And%20More%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'New%20Nostradamus'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hamilton-Parker's%20popularity%20soared%20last%20year%20after%20he%20warned%20of%20an%20imminent%20threat%20on%20Mr%20Trump%20just%20two%20days%20before%20a%20gunman%20fired%20at%20him%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20always%20been%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20that%20there%20would%20be%20an%20attempt%20on%20Trump's%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20warned%20the%20self-described%20seer%20in%20his%20July%202024%20prediction%20roundup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hamilton-Parker%20claims%20to%20have%20visited%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%20in%20his%2020s%20where%20he%20learnt%20the%20ancient%20Indian%20prophecy%20methods%20and%20got%20inspired%20by%20local%20astrologists%20before%20opening%20his%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20nicknamed%20after%20Nostradamus%2C%20a%20French%20astrologer%20and%20physician%20who%20lived%20in%20the%201500s%20and%20predicted%20some%20of%20the%20modern-day%20epochal%20moments%20such%20as%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20rise%20to%20power%2C%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742000880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjfh6tb1_as_625x300_15_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchilling-prediction-made-by-new-nostradamus-with-india-link-comes-true-7926328%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Craig%20Hamilton-Parker%20is%20renowned%20for%20using%20Nadi%20astrology%2C%20a%20prophecy%20method%20with%20roots%20in%20ancient%20India%20to%20predict%20major%20global%20events.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intel's%20new%20CEO%20Lip-Bu%20Tan%20gets%20pay%20package%20valued%20at%20about%20%2469%20million%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742000516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fintel-s-new-ceo-lip-bu-tan-gets-pay-package-valued-at-about-69-million-125031500041_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tan%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20buy%20%2425%20million%20in%20Intel%20shares%20in%20the%20first%2030%20days%20of%20taking%20the%20job%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fintel-s-new-ceo-lip-bu-tan-gets-pay-package-valued-at-a