Nine%20Democrats%20voted%20to%20avoid%20a%20filibuster%2C%20despite%20strong%20objections%20from%20others%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERepublicans%20can%20now%20focus%20on%20their%20sweeping%20border%20and%20tax%20cut%20legislation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESenators%20voted%20on%20Friday%20to%20avert%20a%20government%20shutdown%20just%20hours%20before%20it%20would%20occur%2C%20sending%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20legislation%20that%20would%20slash%20non-defense%20spending%20and%20boost%20the%20Pentagon's%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20vote%20was%2054%20to%2046.%20Only%20one%20Democratic%20lawmaker%2C%20Sen.%20Jeanne%20Shaheen%20of%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20joined%20almost%20all%20Republicans%20in%20passing%20the%20bill.%20Sen.%20Angus%20King%2C%20an%20independent%20from%20Maine%20who%20caucuses%20with%20Democrats%2C%20also%20voted%20for%20the%20bill.%20Sen.%20Rand%20Paul%20of%20Kentucky%2C%20a%20Republican%2C%20voted%20against%20the%20funding%20legislation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20announced%20Thursday%20night%20that%20he%20would%20support%20allowing%20the%20bill%20to%20progress%2C%20breaking%20a%20filibuster%20and%20its%2060-vote%20threshold.%20Nine%20Democrats%20and%20King%20joined%20nearly%20every%20Republican%20to%20advance%20the%20bill%20to%20its%20final%20simple-majority%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikely%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20Democratic%20votes%20moving%20the%20bill%20forward%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20John%20Thune%20allowed%20Democrats%20to%20vote%20on%20three%20different%20amendments%20to%20the%20funding%20bill.%20All%20of%20them%20failed%20to%20pass%2C%20including%20a%20measure%20by%20Sen.%20Chris%20Van%20Hollen%20of%20Maryland%2C%20a%20Democrat%2C%20which%20would%20have%20effectively%20shut%20down%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%2C%20which%20is%20effectively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-musk-doge-head-address-legal-fight-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eled%20by%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20passing%20the%20government%20funding%20bill%2C%20senators%20are%20expected%20to%20pass%20a%20bipartisan%20fix%20to%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20funding%20bill%20that%20would%20have%20required%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20to%20cut%20%241%20billion%20out%20of%20its%20budget.%20The%20House%20would%20need%20to%20pass%20that%20legislation%20when%20they%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-usaid-funding-government-shutdown-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20have%20begun%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Saturday%20morning%20if%20Congress%20failed%20to%20pass%20new%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20major%20victory%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20sign%20the%20legislation%20shortly%2C%20and%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson.%20Johnson%20essentially%20jammed%20Senate%20Democrats%20by%20passing%20the%20bill%20through%20the%20House%20on%20a%20near-party%20line%20vote.%20He%20then%20sent%20lawmakers%20home%2C%20daring%20Schumer%20and%20Democrats%20to%20vote%20down%20the%20legislation%20and%20cause%20a%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongratulations%20to%20Chuck%20Schumer%20for%20doing%20the%20right%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20Took%20'guts'%20and%20courage!%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Friday%20morning%20before%20the%20vote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20big%20Tax%20Cuts%2C%20L.A.%20fire%20fix%2C%20Debt%20Ceiling%20Bill%2C%20and%20so%20much%20more%2C%20is%20coming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cedbf492-b8f1-405c-912c-987485aa8362%5C%22%3EDissent%20among%20Democrats%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20many%20Democrats%20are%20furious%20with%20Schumer%20for%20pushing%20to%20advance%20the%20bill.%20They%20view%20the%20leg