0was%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bvote%20to%20turn%20YOUR%20taxpayer%20dollars%20into%20Trump%20%26amp%3B%20Elon's%20personal%20slush%20funds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2254418ce8-2cac-40cf-910f-f700fb3a50ce%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERepublicans%20still%20have%20tough%20votes%20ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20extends%20government%20funding%20through%20September%2030.%20Its%20passage%20means%20Trump%20and%20Republicans%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20a%20potential%20shutdown%20as%20they%20enter%20the%20thick%20of%20negotiations%20for%20their%20massive%20border%20security%20and%20tax%20bill.%20Johnson%20has%20pledged%20to%20send%20Trump%20legislation%20by%20Easter%2C%20an%20ambitious%20timeline%20requiring%20both%20houses%20to%20reach%20an%20agreement%20soon.%20The%20House%20and%20Senate%20are%20still%20negotiating%20whether%20the%20legislation%20will%20include%20Trump's%20tax%20cuts%20or%20if%20they%20punt%20that%20issue%20to%20another%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20final%20fiscal%20deadline%20looming.%20Congress%20still%20has%20to%20raise%20the%20debt%20limit%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%20possibly%20as%20early%20as%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-passes-government-funding-shutdown-avoided-doge-elon-musk-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741991190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d340f069253ccddf99366c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-passes-government-funding-shutdown-avoided-doge-elon-musk-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senate%20Democrats%20decided%20not%20to%20block%20a%20GOP-led%20funding%20bill%2C%20which%20many%20have%20said%20fails%20to%20do%20enough%20to%20rein%20in%20Elon%20Musk's%20DOGE.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths%2