charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ffefaae09223df2badd59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOutside%20the%20JPMorgan%20headquarters%20in%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEmployees%20are%20waiting%20to%20hear%20how%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20will%20enforce%20its%20return-to-office%20mandate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20searching%20for%20clues%2C%20in%20one%20instance%20sharing%20a%20leaked%20document%20in%20a%20group%20chat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmployees%20also%20shared%20info%20about%20location%20and%20productivity%20tracking%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20private%20group%20chat%20formed%20after%20JPMorgan's%20January%20announcement%20that%20all%20employees%20would%20be%20called%20back%20to%20the%20office%20full-time%2C%20a%20few%20hundred%20people%20have%20turned%20to%20the%20forum%20to%20air%20their%20concerns%2C%20vent%20about%20the%20changes%2C%20and%20share%20tidbits%20of%20intel%20from%20their%20respective%20corners%20of%20the%20bank%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20understand%20the%20bank's%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20active%26quot%3B%20chat%20gets%20upward%20of%20100%20messages%20a%20day%2C%20according%20to%20one%20member%2C%20a%20JPMorgan%20employee%20of%208%20years%2C%20who%20talked%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20many%20Signal%20chats%20and%20Reddit%20threads%20that%20JPMorgan%20employees%20are%20turning%20to%20as%20unofficial%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20groups%26quot%3B%20for%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20depressingly%20small%20amount%20of%20official%20information%20within%20JPMC%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20expressing%20their%20concern%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20emails%20about%20what's%20happening.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20go%20find%20the%20information%2C%20it%20is%20not%20being%20broadcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20a%20document%20with%20JPMorgan%20branding%20was%20shared%20with%20the%20group%20and%20caused%20an%20instant%20hubbub%2C%20a%20different%20member%20of%20the%20chat%20told%20BI%2C%20which%20viewed%20the%20contents.%20It%20appeared%20to%20be%20an%20outline%20of%20steps%20of%20escalation%20for%20employees%20who%20don't%20meet%20RTO%20mandates%2C%20including%20a%20lower%20number%20of%20non-attendance%20warnings%20before%20possible%20termination%20for%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20document%20or%20determine%20who%20dropped%20it%20in%20the%20encrypted%20chat.%20It%20is%20also%20unclear%20if%20it%20represents%20current%20or%20future%20bank%20policy.%20What%20is%20clear%20based%20on%20chat%20members'%20reactions%20to%20the%206-page%20outline%20is%20that%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20employees%20are%20hungry%20for%20any%20clues%20to%20how%20the%20bank%20will%20enforce%20its%205-days-in-office%20policy%2C%20which%20began%20rolling%20out%20March%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20JPMorgan%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20document%20but%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20employees%20are%20not%20meeting%20the%20expectations%2C%20there%20will%20be%20ramifications%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20any%20other%20performance%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20are%20also%20eager%20to%20understand%20how%20their%20attendance%20is%20monitored.%20Some%20worry%20that%20company%20tracking%20methods%20might%20not%20correctly%20record%20their%20hours%20or%20productivity%20%E2%80%94%20putting%20them%20at%20risk%20of%20potential%20enforcement.%20Others%20feel%20the%20RTO%20mandates%20and%20attendance%20recording%20measures%20are%20overkill.%20The%20employees%20were%20granted%20anonymity%20by%20BI%20to%20discuss%20internal%20company%20information%20without%20professional%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20JPMorgan%20tech%20VP%20told%20BI%2C%20sarcastically%2C%20that%20they%20thought%20the%20%26quot%3Bbabysitting%20was%20ending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20group%20chat%20have%20been%20sharing%20intel%20about%20tools%20for%20surveilling%20employee%20location%20and%20productivity.%20An%20employee%20who%20BI%20did%20not%20speak%20with%20shared%20that%20their%20manager%20had%20shown%20them%20a%20new%20tool%20with%20a%20heat%20map%20that%20shows%20how%20productive%20employees%20are%20based%20on%20the%20items%20worked%20on%20per%20hour.%20A%20technologist%20who%20has%20direct%20knowledge%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20tool%20that%20tracked%20productivity%20per%20hour.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20widely%20it%20had%20been%20rolled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20impossible%20to%20put%20a%20number%20on%20productivity%20on%20a%20minute-by-minute%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20the%20group%20chat%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%20much%20of%20what%20we%20do%20is%20about%20communication%2C%20learning%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20investing.%20The%20only%20quantifiable%20measures%20take%20weeks%20to%20materialize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20firmwide%20heat%20map%20that%20tracks%20individual%20production%20volumes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20several%20years%20now%2C%20we%20have%20had%20a%20transparent%20attendance%20tool%20that%20is%20available%20for%20all%20employees%20and%20managers%20to%20view%20and%20record%20their%20time%2C%20including%20vacation%20days%2C%20sick%20days%2C%20work%20from%20home%2C%20and%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20engineer%20and%20the%20technologist%20both%20described%20color-coded%20calendars%20on%20manager%20dashboards%20that%20show%20employees'%20attendance%2C%20highlighting%20patterns%20such%20as%20requesting%20to%20work%20from%20home%20every%20Friday%20or%20calling%20in%20sick%20every%20Thursday.%20The%20chat-group%20document%20mentioned%20such%20patterns%20as%20grounds%